     <h2><font color="#000080"><!-- 2004-09-02 -->
	 <a href="http://davetravel.scripting.com/2004/09/20#a74" 
                     title="external link">
	 Seattle: Through New Eyes
	 </a></font>
     </h2>
    

	<p>
    <a href="http://davetravel.scripting.com/2004/09/20#a74">Dave's Travels - A walk on the Seattle waterfront</a>.&nbsp; It is often inspiring for me to see a familiar place throught the eyes of someone looking at it for the first time.&nbsp; Dave Winer is making that gift to us as he discovers his surroundings during a stay in Seattle.&nbsp; It gives me a different appreciation of where I am (and has me reaching for my camera).
    </p>
